Unite Test Case for MTK bandwidth control module (BWC)


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
bwc_test provides the unit test cases for libbwc.so.
libbwc.so optimizes the bus access latency in multimedia scenarios to meet realtime 
requirement. BWC is required for all MTK multimedia middleware implementation including
camera and video middlewares.


HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
It needs the following library from AOSP:
1.  liblog.so
2.  libcutils.so



HOW TO USE IT?
==============

The developer can launch bwc_test with adb shell and check the console output for the unit 
test result.

All the source code of this library were written by MediaTek co..
